            <p>More than half of our site's visitors are on mobile devices. That's why we introduced the email field to allow us to send the Not By AI badges to the users' inboxes to eliminate the need for them to download badges on their phones and then transfer them to a desktop for use. It is also handy when your browser blocks direct downloads or if, for any reason, the download doesn't happen as expected. As an added bonus, it allows the users to retrieve the badges conveniently in their inbox if they are unable to locate them. Additionally, it provides us with an opportunity to communicate digitally with our users through newsletters and announcements, as it enables us to build an email list. It's important to note that an email is only included in our list when a user checks the marketing permission checkbox.</p>
